  "text": "It is possible to use previous joint sentiment topic models, such as ASUM [CITATION_1] and JST [CITATION_2] , for the filtering purpose. Note that ASUM and JST output word distributions for each pair of sentiment and aspect; hence, ASUM and JST are in effect both sentiment classifier and filter:",
